# CS Cliq ‚Äî inbox architecture (Portal admin)

## Product rule (do not mix lanes in one flat list for CEOs)

| Surface | Who | Contents |
|---------|-----|----------|
| **Inbox ‚Üí Direct** | Victor, Raul, Javi | 1:1 DMs between directors, **Admin** (Sevitha ops contact), groups **`all_ceos`** (label **CEOs**) and **`ceo_liaison`** (label **Sev + CEOs**) with member chips |
| **Inbox ‚Üí Staff ops** | Victor, Raul, Javi | Shared **Sevitha‚Üîworker** thread per staff member (Roberto, instructors, support). Not personal CEO‚Üîworker DMs |
| **Inbox** (single list) | Sevitha (ops admin) | Full staff roster + own ops lane |
| **Channels ‚Üí Leads / Staff** | Admin / CEOs | Group broadcast channels (session leads, staff pools). **No** `all_ceos` / `ceo_liaison` here for directors ‚Äî those live in **Direct** |
| **Staff dashboard** | Workers / leads | One row **Admin** only ‚Äî never surface director names |

## UI copy (CEO trio)

- **Direct hint:** leadership circle (directors, CEO groups, Admin).
- **Staff ops hint:** shared Sevitha‚Üîstaff line; replies signed with sender name.
- Do not re-add **Shared ops** pill when the **Staff ops** tab is active (redundant).
- Suppress chat toasts when CS Cliq inbox is already open (`portalAdminDmShouldSuppressIncomingChatNotify`).

## Data / routing

- Ops worker thread: `portal_staff_dm_ensure_ops_thread` / Sevitha participant ‚Äî lane `inboxLane: 'ops'`.
- CEO personal DM with another director: normal DM thread ‚Äî **Direct** tab only.
- God-mode send-as-Admin: `portalCeoGodModeAdmin` + RPC `portal_staff_dm_insert_ops_admin_message` (migration `20260629120000_portal_dm_insert_ops_admin_message.sql`).
- Incoming call ring: only the intended peer (not all directors on staff calls).

## Key modules

- `portal_cs_cliq_admin_inbox.js` ‚Äî Direct / Staff ops split, lane hints, director groups in Direct.
- `portal_cs_cliq_management_inbox.js` ‚Äî `buildSections`, ops vs mine lanes.
- `portal_cs_cliq_admin_channels.js` ‚Äî Leads / Staff channels; hide empty CEOs tab.
- `admin_dashboard.html` ‚Äî `portalAdminDmRenderList`, group labels (`CEOs`, `Sev + CEOs`), member chips.

When changing inbox behaviour, preserve lane separation and update hints/labels together.
